{"tid":1138103,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"家朗 羽毛球大勝 林丹 入決賽","createTime":"2019-05-04T10:06:45.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-04T10:11:25.000Z","uid":54373,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"b0a1ab30a216d6de40107d8164f121cf6934f92b","tid":1138103,"uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-04T10:06:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n世界排名16位的伍家朗重返賽場，於新西蘭公開賽愈戰愈勇，殺入男單4強後遇上排名高4位的「超級丹」林丹，最終這港將以局數21：13、21：11，僅用上34分鐘便爆冷淘汰對手，殺入決賽。家朗對上一次對陣林丹，是2018年德國公開賽，當時同以直落兩局擊敗對方，目前雙方4戰對賽，家朗已累積3勝1負，不負林丹殺手之名。"},{"pid":"c35fb9c698f659c743aaa52fa2dd048bedc6936a","tid":1138103,"uid":166474,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-04T10:11:25.000Z","msg":"林丹仲想打奧運？石宇奇一定出，諶龍衛冕冠軍，點都冇佢份啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}